imdb.plot outline: A fate pushes off two women - 19-years-old Liliya and 38-years-old Irina. Each of them has in life a secret that they try to unriddle. Their relations pass all phases - from mutual hostility to the inexplicable liking. Elusive, and sometimes brightly showing up likeness in everything becomes the noticeable surrounding. But neither their nearest surroundings nor they for the time being do not guess that they are a mother and daughter.
